<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xml:lang="en"><generator uri="https://jekyllrb.com/" version="4.4.1">Jekyll</generator><link href="https://xiaojz9.github.io/feed.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml"/><link href="https://xiaojz9.github.io/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" hreflang="en"/><updated>2026-02-28T20:22:45+00:00</updated><id>https://xiaojz9.github.io/feed.xml</id><title type="html">blank</title><subtitle>PhD Student in Mechanical Engineering at UCI. Research on micro-scale flow boiling, multiphase heat transfer, and computer vision. </subtitle><entry><title type="html">Realm’s Night Rain Dreamlike</title><link href="https://xiaojz9.github.io/blog/2026/Realm's-Night-Rain-Dreamlike/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Realm’s Night Rain Dreamlike"/><published>2026-02-28T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2026-02-28T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://xiaojz9.github.io/blog/2026/Realm&apos;s%20Night%20Rain%20Dreamlike</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://xiaojz9.github.io/blog/2026/Realm&apos;s-Night-Rain-Dreamlike/"><![CDATA[<p>Live on, and live well.<br/> “好好活着”</p> <hr/> <style>.drama-gallery{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:25px;margin-top:30px}.drama-item{text-align:center}.drama-item img{width:100%;border-radius:12px;transition:transform .3s ease}.drama-item img:hover{transform:scale(1.05)}.drama-video{grid-column:1 / -1}.drama-video video{width:100%;border-radius:16px}.drama-title{font-weight:600;margin-top:10px}.drama-desc{font-size:.9rem;color:#555;margin-top:5px}</style> <div class="drama-gallery"> <div class="drama-item drama-video"> <video controls=""> <source src="/assets/video/JHYYZSM1.mp4" type="video/mp4"/> </video> <div class="drama-desc"> 吾妻尚年少 </div> </div> <div class="drama-item drama-video"> <video controls=""> <source src="/assets/video/JHYYZSM2.mp4" type="video/mp4"/> </video> <div class="drama-desc"> 怜语慰卿卿 </div> </div> </div> <hr/>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="personal"/><category term="drama"/><summary type="html"><![CDATA[江湖夜雨终似梦]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Kill To Love</title><link href="https://xiaojz9.github.io/blog/2026/photo-gallery/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Kill To Love"/><published>2026-02-28T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2026-02-28T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://xiaojz9.github.io/blog/2026/photo-gallery</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://xiaojz9.github.io/blog/2026/photo-gallery/"><![CDATA[<p>When the pear blossoms bloom again, may we be reunited.<br/> “望来年梨花再开我们再重聚”</p> <hr/> <style>.drama-gallery{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:25px;margin-top:30px}.drama-item{text-align:center}.drama-item img{width:100%;border-radius:12px;transition:transform .3s ease}.drama-item img:hover{transform:scale(1.05)}.drama-video{grid-column:1 / -1}.drama-video video{width:100%;border-radius:16px}.drama-title{font-weight:600;margin-top:10px}.drama-desc{font-size:.9rem;color:#555;margin-top:5px}.bili-wrapper{position:relative;padding-bottom:56.25%;height:0;overflow:hidden;border-radius:12px}.bili-wrapper iframe{position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%}</style> <div class="drama-gallery"> <div class="drama-item drama-video"> <video controls=""> <source src="/assets/video/KTL1.mp4" type="video/mp4"/> </video> <div class="drama-desc"> Who is calling me Shu He now? The son of a salt merchant, the orphaned heir of General Duan’s fallen house, an assassin ablaze with hatred— </div> </div> <div class="drama-item drama-video"> <video controls=""> <source src="/assets/video/KTL2.mp4" type="video/mp4"/> </video> <div class="drama-desc"> Or the Jibei agent who has calculated every step? </div> </div> <div class="drama-item drama-video"> <video controls=""> <source src="/assets/video/KTL3.mp4" type="video/mp4"/> </video> <div class="drama-desc"> Don’t cry. Your tears wound me more than a sword ever could. </div> </div> <div class="drama-item drama-video"> <video controls=""> <source src="/assets/video/KTL4.mp4" type="video/mp4"/> </video> <div class="drama-desc"> You lied to me… all my life. </div> </div> <div class="drama-item drama-video"> <div class="bili-wrapper"> <iframe src="https://player.bilibili.com/player.html?bvid=BV1BeByBHEdK&amp;page=1" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""> </iframe> </div> </div> <div class="drama-item drama-video"> <div class="bili-wrapper"> <iframe src="https://player.bilibili.com/player.html?bvid=BV1PqxKzkEty&amp;page=1" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""> </iframe> </div> </div> <div class="drama-item"> <a href="/assets/img/IMG_1.png" data-lightbox="drama" data-title="枯荣流转总在天"> <img src="/assets/img/IMG_1.png"/> </a> <div class="drama-title">枯荣流转总在天</div> <div class="drama-desc"> Withering and flourishing are all decreed by fate. </div> </div> <div class="drama-item"> <a href="/assets/img/IMG_2.png" data-lightbox="drama" data-title="我不想再提从前了"> <img src="/assets/img/IMG_2.png"/> </a> <div class="drama-title">我不想再提从前了</div> <div class="drama-desc"> I don’t want to talk about the past anymore. </div> </div> <div class="drama-item"> <a href="/assets/img/IMG_3.png" data-lightbox="drama" data-title="再来一次吧"> <img src="/assets/img/IMG_3.png"/> </a> <div class="drama-title">再来一次吧</div> <div class="drama-desc"> If only we could try again. </div> </div> </div> <hr/>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="personal"/><category term="drama"/><summary type="html"><![CDATA[紫陌红尘]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">青色陆地之下</title><link href="https://xiaojz9.github.io/blog/2025/c1/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="青色陆地之下"/><published>2025-03-20T20:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2025-03-20T20:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://xiaojz9.github.io/blog/2025/c1</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://xiaojz9.github.io/blog/2025/c1/"><![CDATA[<style>.poetry-block{max-width:800px;margin:60px auto;line-height:1.9;font-size:1.05rem;text-align:left}.poetry-block p{margin-bottom:26px}.cn{display:block;margin-top:6px;color:#888;font-size:.95rem}.image-block{max-width:800px;margin:50px auto}.image-block img{width:100%;border-radius:12px;display:block}</style> <div class="poetry-block"> <p> The love that could not be spoken from between his lips<br/> had never once touched the sun. <span class="cn"> 从他唇间无法宣之于口的爱尚未触及太阳 </span> </p> <p> Not because it had dried —<br/> but because not a single drop had ever evaporated.<br/> It remained as it was,<br/> a bead of water rippling endlessly within his heart. <span class="cn"> 缘于一滴都未曾干涸，以原本的模样荡漾在心间的水滴 </span> </p> <p> Yet if it were to remain still,<br/> that surging love would swallow even breath itself —<br/> drowning, suffocating, consuming him whole. <span class="cn"> 虽然如若静止不动，那汹涌的爱意会连呼吸都吞没殆尽悬溺窒息 </span> </p> <p> And so, his love began in his eyes,<br/> spilling forth. <span class="cn"> 因此爱意始于他的眼底，倾泻而出 </span> </p> <p> After he had dyed every inch of ancestral land<br/> into a river-deep emerald tide,<br/> his love still did not wither. <span class="cn"> 当他将祖先留下来的所有土地都浸染成了江河般的碧绿色彩后，他的爱仍未枯竭耗尽 </span> </p> <p> In the end,<br/> he buried his own head beneath this terrain —<br/> neither river nor earth, but a sensual continent of longing —<br/> and ceased to breathe. <span class="cn"> 于是他最终将自己的头颅深埋进这片既不能称之为江河又不能称之为大地的情色陆地之下停止了呼吸 </span> </p> <p> He clasped in his palm<br/> the long-awaited arrival of peace. <span class="cn"> 将终于降临的安宁紧紧握于掌心 </span> </p> </div> <div class="image-block"> <img src="/assets/img/m1.png"/> </div> <div class="image-block"> <img src="/assets/img/m2.png"/> </div> <div class="image-block"> <img src="/assets/img/m3.png"/> </div> <div class="image-block"> <img src="/assets/img/m4.png"/> </div>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="personal"/><category term="comics"/><summary type="html"><![CDATA[푸른 뭍 아래로 by 금기, 이선의]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Sunset Boulevard</title><link href="https://xiaojz9.github.io/blog/2025/riluodadao/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Sunset Boulevard"/><published>2025-03-20T20:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2025-03-20T20:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://xiaojz9.github.io/blog/2025/riluodadao</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://xiaojz9.github.io/blog/2025/riluodadao/"><![CDATA[<blockquote> <p>高原的氧气稀薄，让章决呼吸困难。陈泊桥三个字一共二十五笔，章决每落一笔，指间到手腕都酸楚一遍。<br/> <em>The thin air of the highlands left Zhang Jue breathless. Chen Boqiao’s name requires twenty-five strokes.With each stroke he wrote, a dull ache spread from his fingers to his wrist.</em></p> </blockquote> <hr/> <blockquote> <p>在罗什的草坪边暗自寻觅陈泊桥的章决，拿着就诊卡站在医院前厅的章决，在长明灯池边写下陈泊桥名字的章决也被好好储存起来了。放进一个很好、很美的，能融化痛楚的房间。<br/> <em>The Zhang Jue who once looked for Chen Boqiao in silence by Roche’s lawn, who stood alone in the hospital foyer clutching his registration card, who wrote Chen Boqiao’s name by the pool of everlasting lamps — he has been stored away, tenderly, in a room that is kind and beautiful, a room warm enough to dissolve all sorrow.</em></p> </blockquote> <hr/> <blockquote> <p>”亚联盟不配审判你“<br/> <em>“The Alliance is not worthy of judging you.”</em></p> </blockquote>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="personal"/><category term="novel"/><summary type="html"><![CDATA[日落大道 by 卡比丘]]></summary></entry></feed>